The Kaduna government says a breakdown of law and order was averted in Kachia town, headquarters of Kachia Local Government Area. Tension gripped the community after the killing of one Hamidu Nura by one Abba Muhammad. Samuel Aruwan, Commissioner for Internal Security, in a statement said an irate mob mobilized themselves and captured Abba Muhammad. Muhammad died after he was attacked with knives, clubs and other dangerous weapons. Aruwan confirmed the situation is being investigated by security agencies. The commissioner assured that the safety of lives and property of the people remains paramount.